OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA settled
OL,6,Fnight with light winds and clear
OL,7,Fspells allowing mist and fog to form
OL,8,Fin some places. Mild in urban areas
OL,9,Fbut cooler in rural spots.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FA hot day with some cloudy
OL,12,Fperiods during the morning followed by
OL,13,Fa bright and sunny afternoon. Cooler
OL,14,Falong the coast with a refreshing sea
OL,15,Fbreeze.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,18,FLargely bright and sunny throughout,
OL,19,Fand notably hot on Monday and Tuesday.
OL,20,FTemperatures may start to decrease
OL,21,Ffrom Wednesday as it becomes breezier.
